Yes. This is a genuinely good app idea.

It is simple, addictive, and weirdly hard to stop using because it turns “what’s my favorite Pokémon?” into a clean little ranking game instead of an impossible open-ended question.

Core concept

You are always shown:
	•	Current Champion on one side
	•	Challenger on the other

Then you choose:
	•	Swipe right = challenger wins
	•	Swipe left = champion stays
	•	Maybe / On Deck = save challenger for later

So instead of sorting 1,000+ Pokémon at once, you are just answering one question:

“Do I like this one more than my current favorite?”

That makes the whole thing feel easy.

