Smart algorithm flow

A nice version would work like this:

Early game
	•	broad random comparisons
	•	quickly learn taste zones

Mid game
	•	compare likely contenders
	•	cluster by similar favorites

Late game
	•	repeated tests among top 20
	•	bring back On Deck maybes
	•	tighten ranking confidence

Then show:
	•	“We’re 92% sure your favorite is Gengar.”

That would feel awesome.

